title: Which Star Players Could Be Cut Before Free Agency?
itunes:title: Which Star Players Could Be Cut Before Free Agency?
description:
A room filled with heroes- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler & Colleen Wolfe are all back together again! The heroes discuss Colleen’s Cardi B rap video, which became an internet sensation (2:00); An addition to the ATN Trophy Cabinet- thanks to a thoughtful and talented listener (5:30); The latest news from around the league, including Frank Reich being introduced as the Colts’ head coach (10:00), Kam Chancellor’s playing status for 2018 (13:00) and a closer look at one of Marc’s Super Bowl Sandwich Props (24:00); Dan creates the pilot episode of the Theology Podcast (28:00); The heroes discuss which prominent veterans could be cut before the new league year begins.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
